org.eclipse.collections.api.tuple

Interface Pair<T1,T2>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Comparable<Pair<T1,T2>>, Serializable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Twin<T>

    public interface Pair<T1,T2>
extends Serializable, Comparable<Pair<T1,T2>>
    A Pair is a container that holds two related objects. It is the equivalent of an Association in Smalltalk, or an implementation of Map.Entry in the JDK.
